\sum_{k=o}^{\infty} x^k
\frac{1}{1-x}
|x|<1
\frac{1}{1-x^2}
\frac{1}{1-x^2}=\frac{1}{1-x}\frac{1}{1+x}, x\neq\pm1
\sum_{k=o}^{\infty} \frac{f^k(0)}{k!}x^k
\frac1{1-x^2}=\frac1{1-(x^2)}=1+(x^2)+(x^2)^2+\ldots=1+x^2+x^4+\ldots
\frac1{1+x}=\frac1{1-(-x)}=1+(-x)+(-x)^2+(-x)^3+\ldots=1-x+x^2-x^3+\ldots
\frac1{1-x^2}=\frac12\left(\frac1{1-x}+\frac1{1+x}\right)= \frac12\left(1+x+x^2+\ldots+1-x+x^2-x^3+\ldots\right)=
=\frac12\left(2+2x^2+2x^4+\ldots\right)=1+x^2+x^4+\ldots
